title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – May 6 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – May 6 2022
description:
Frank Siller, founder of Tunnel to Towers -- and Jennie Taylor, a T2T Ambassador, mother of seven, and surviving spouse -- join Clay and Buck. C&B talk about posters in their boyhood rooms, new movies. Mother's Day special: Clay and Buck's moms, Liz Travis and Jane Sexton, join their boys on the air for the first time. Spunky sides of both (Jane on her days performing in a commercial with Ralph Macchio and Liz quipping about her lovely Southern accent, "This voice is a dying art") as well as C&B childhood secrets spill out.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
